						<p>Chōḻa, Parāntaka I, 29th year = A.D. 936.</p>						

						<p>Gift of 90 sheep for a lamp to the temple of Tiruttāṭakēśvarattu-Mahādēva at Tiruppanandāḷ a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> in Maṇṇi-nāḍu on the north bank, by Iṟaiyāṉ Mādēvaṉ a <hi rend="italic">uḍaiyāṉ</hi> of Kumāramaṅgalam in Ambar-nāḍu.</p>						

